snippet.title: Let's School - Console Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
We're thrilled to finally announce the release date for Let's School on console! 🔥🎉
Let's School is scheduled to release July 16th on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X/S and Xbox One.

Join our community and follow us on social media for more exciting news about this cozy school sim:
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/dZAQjFp
Twitter: https://twitter.com/letsschool_
Subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/LetsSchool/

#letsschool #gaming #indiegame #cozy #simulation
